build_index — Scan the pret/pokeyellow GB source (home/, engine/, scripts/) and
build (or rebuild) the translation work-queue database at dos_port/tools/translation.db.

home/ + engine/ files are categorised simple/complex (swarm jobs); scripts/*.asm
become 'script' category (per-map scripts hand-translated by Claude Code).

Usage:
    dos_port/tools/build_index [--rebuild]

--rebuild  Drop and recreate all tables before inserting. Without this flag,
           only rows whose source_file is not already present are inserted,
           so manually-set statuses survive a re-run.
"""

